						Typical graph shape when quantity decreases then increases,
						but rate is always increasing.
					</shortdescription>
					<!-- TODO description -->
					<latex-image><xi:include href="curves.d/quantity-vs-rate-2.tex" parse="text" /></latex-image>
				</image>
			</figure>

			<figure>
				<caption> Quantity decreasing but rate increasing. </caption>
				<image xml:id="image-curves-quantity-vs-rate-3">
